<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Income Documents Required</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #17a2b8;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .urgent-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .document-list {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .requirements {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #17a2b8;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .deadline {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        ul li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .check-icon {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>📊 Income Documentation Required</h1>
        <p>Additional documents needed to complete your screening</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{applicantName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for submitting your tenant screening application for {{propertyName}}. To complete the income verification portion of your screening, we need additional documentation from you.</p>

        <div class="urgent-notice">
            <h3>⏰ Action Required</h3>
            <p><strong>Application Number:</strong> {{applicationNumber}}</p>
            <p>Your application is currently on hold pending receipt of the required income documents listed below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="document-list">
            <h3>📋 Required Documents</h3>
            <p>Please provide the following documents to verify your income:</p>
            <ul>
                {{#each requiredDocuments}}
                <li><span class="check-icon">☑️</span>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="requirements">
            <h3>📝 Document Requirements</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pay Stubs:</strong> Must be recent (within 60 days) and show year-to-date totals</li>
                <li><strong>Employment Letter:</strong> Must be on company letterhead and include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your job title and employment start date</li>
                        <li>Your current salary or hourly wage</li>
                        <li>Whether employment is full-time, part-time, or contract</li>
                        <li>Contact information for HR verification</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Bank Statements:</strong> Must show consistent income deposits</li>
                <li><strong>Tax Returns:</strong> Required if self-employed (previous year with Schedule C)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="deadline">
            <h3>⚠️ Important Deadline</h3>
            <p><strong>Please submit these documents within 5 business days to avoid application expiration.</strong></p>
            <p>Deadline: {{deadline}}</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{uploadUrl}}" class="button">Upload Documents Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="requirements">
            <h3>📤 How to Submit</h3>
            <p>You can submit your documents in any of the following ways:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Online:</strong> Use the secure upload portal (recommended)</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> Send scanned copies to {{contactEmail}}</li>
                <li><strong>In-Person:</strong> Drop off at our office during business hours</li>
                <li><strong>Fax:</strong> {{faxNumber}} (if available)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="urgent-notice">
            <h3>🔒 Privacy & Security</h3>
            <p>All documents are handled securely and in compliance with privacy laws. Your personal information is protected and will only be used for tenant screening purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Questions?</strong> If you have any questions about the required documents or need assistance with the upload process, please contact us immediately.</p>

        <p>We appreciate your prompt attention to this request and look forward to completing your application.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Property Management Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Property Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Contact us: {{contactPhone}} | {{contactEmail}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
